#grouping: sheet columns/tradesheet

[Adaptiv XVA]FTradingSheet:Incremental PFE =
  Description=Incremental PFE for a specific trade (normally in status Simulated). The original trade set for the PFE calculation is located via the credit balance instrument that has properties matching the trade. The incremental PFE is calculated as the difference between a PFE calculation with the original trade set plus the trade and a PFE calculation with the original trade set. Note that the incremental PFE will be zero if the trade is already included in the original trade set.
  ExtensionAttribute=incrementalPFE
  GroupLabel=PFE
  LabelList=Inc PFE
  Name=Incremental PFE

